{"tid":128060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貪曾收監：20分鐘收監路　夕陽映囚車添落寞","createTime":"2017-02-20T13:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T15:56:46.000Z","uid":408,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f4fe6c90d5f46542be75f67d8005e8abc7e1ae","tid":128060,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001.html&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=923d87f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170220214236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170220214236&h=55957e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在斜陽的映照下，貪曾20分鐘收監之路暢通無阻！下午5時45分，曾蔭權乘坐囚車離開金鐘高等法院，半百記者的閃光燈「射向」車內的曾蔭權，他坐於右邊首排靠窗位置，可清楚看見他煲呔已經除，雙手鎖上手銬的曾蔭權神情呆滯，一直向前望，期間突然轉過臉，一度瞪大雙眼望向左邊車窗，接着又再向前直望。<br />\n<br />\n囚車在10名警員開路下，花費近5分鐘才成功駛出金鐘道。雖然適逢放工繁忙時候，但平時「塞爆」的金鐘和中環一帶道路，竟異常暢通，無警車護送的囚車，經過畢打街，轉入干諾道中向西隧方向行駛，途經國金一期、信德中心，曾蔭權可望到街景行人，但無人會留意到，這輛囚車中坐着前特首曾蔭權爵士，當囚車駛向西隧時，正好迎着西落的夕陽疾駛，只可惜，曾蔭權風光不再。<br />\n<br />\n囚車駛出西隧後，經過大角咀亦一路暢通無阻，約20分鐘已抵達荔枝角收押所，收押所門外亦有近20名記者守候，警方則在行人道架起圍欄，囚車順利直駛入收押所，通道大閘隨即關上。今次押送貪曾的囚車，在相距進入監室的通道入口近4米位置停下，附近亦未有裝上任何遮擋設施，記者可清楚拍下他落車一刻，6名懲教員招呼曾下車後，曾刻意側身避全貌落入記者鏡頭，他將鎖上手銬的雙手緊緊貼近身體，快步進入通道，囚犯的生活正式開始。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170220214236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170220214236&h=e16f8281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n囚車花近5分鐘才成功駛出金鐘高等法院。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170220214236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170220214236&h=604ae7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n囚車駛經信德中心，平時繁忙道路今日異常暢通。（左錦鴻攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170220214236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170220214236&h=5152d0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n囚車駛向西隧時，剛好迎着西落的夕陽。（左錦鴻攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_05b.jpg?20170220214236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170220210925379-0220_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20170220214236&h=d077b5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n囚車駛出西隧後，直朝荔枝角收押所方向駛去。（左錦鴻攝）"},{"pid":"85a2a923f80bc019627cea1596f474d455652890","tid":128060,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"啲措詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb6abd9cd860d384ade469a73ca949b9c2e0d2d","tid":128060,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c677543b54a7ec831a141ea27d991356ffeb7f3","tid":128060,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"斜陽裏 氣魄更壯<br />\n斜陽落下 心中不必驚慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7118d0c9009db82c7